I think there has been an
intentional obstruction

00:47:52.110 --> 00:47:54.370 align:middle line:84%
of the truth in this
particular area or else

00:47:54.370 --> 00:47:55.875 align:middle line:90%
at least willful ignorance.

00:47:55.875 --> 00:47:57.250 align:middle line:84%
I personally go
way out of my way

